      <title>前《中国日报》编辑胡锡进因发表经济言论被社交媒体封禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/ex-china-editor-hu-banned-on-social-media-after-post-on-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国官媒《环球时报》前总编辑胡锡进因发表针对世界第二大经济体的争议性言论而被禁止在社交媒体上发帖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/ex-china-editor-hu-banned-on-social-media-after-post-on-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 10:30:10 GMT</pubDate>
